title: What if You Lost Your Job?
itunes:title: What if You Lost Your Job?
description:
An 8 year old made $26 Million this year on YouTube. It's a fact that the world is changing quickly and the job market is changing just as fast. In this episode, I challenge you to think outside of the box for ways to make money because if you don't, you might be out of a job soon!

Join the IronMind60 Challenge here http://ironmind60.com/
